We teach acoustic, electric, and classical guitar, bass, piano, voice, drums, violin, sax, Greek bouzouki, and more! Our store sells and repairs brand name musical instruments and accessories at the lowest prices in Toronto - guaranteed! Call 416-406-5355 for a free consultation today.
